{"lemma":"جُبَّيْ","slug":"جُبَّيْ","root":"ج.ب.ب","root_slug":"ج-ب-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-ب-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جُبّ","root":"جبب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":9},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4911","n5024","n5025"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cistern, well"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pit, fosse, cavity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pothole, chuckhole"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to sever, to notch, to cut, to chop off, to lop off, to truncate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to beat down the leaves"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to castrate entirely, to cut off a man's penis"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fructify the fruit palm"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to surpass, to overcome, to vanquish"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of جَبَّ (jabba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *gubb-.\nCompare Classical Syriac ܓܘܒܐ (gubbā), Aramaic גב (/⁠gōb⁠/, “pit, moat”), Hebrew גֵּב (gev), Akkadian 𒁺𒁍 (/⁠gubbu⁠/, “reservoir, cistern”), Tigrinya ጋው (gawə, “cistern”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4911","headword_ar":"جُبِّىٌّ","root":"jb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[app. a contraction of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubabiY~N","text_ar":"جُبَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAbiY~N","text_ar":"جِبَابِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A seller of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAb","text_ar":"جِبَاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jub~apN","text_ar":"جُبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. (K.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":372}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n5024","headword_ar":"جَبَى","root":"jbw and jbY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabayotu","text_ar":"جَبَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, Er-Rághib,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaY","text_ar":"جَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) said by MF to be unknown, and also, because neither the second nor the third radical is a faucial letter, unreasonable, but mentioned by Sb, though held by him to be of weak authority, and mentioned also by IAar, as extr., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abaY","text_ar":"اَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA^obaY","text_ar":"يَاْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaA","text_ar":"جَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabawotu","text_ar":"جَبَوْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ks, S, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) inf. n. [of the first and second]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaboYN","text_ar":"جَبْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, K) and [probably of the last only]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabFA","text_ar":"جَبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibFA","text_ar":"جِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jubFA","text_ar":"جُبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of the last, but whether in the first or the second of the senses here following is not shown,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibowapN","text_ar":"جِبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K; [or this last has a different application, explained below;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"water in a trough or tank for beasts &c. [Ks, S, K, Er-Rághib.) ―         -b2-  And (hence, metaphorically, Er-Rághib, TA) the first of these verbs, (S, Mgh, Msb, K, Er-Rághib,) and the second, (K,) and the third; (S, Msb, TA;) inf. n. (of the first, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAyapN","text_ar":"جِبَايَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K, Er-Rághib) and (of the last, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibaAwapN","text_ar":"جِبَاوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabowN","text_ar":"جَبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [and probably"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jibowapN","text_ar":"جِبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, which see above]; (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected"},{"kind":"text","text":"the [tax called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaraAj","text_ar":"خَرَاج"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K, Er-Rághib,) and [other] property. (Msb, TA.) The last of these verbs is said in the S to be originally with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", though pronounced without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but IB says that this is not the case, and that it has not been heard with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaAhu Alqawoma","text_ar":"جَبَاهُ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected it from the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (M, K, * TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaY minohumo","text_ar":"جَبَى مِنْهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected from them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, K, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaA","text_ar":"جَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaY","text_ar":"جَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (TA,) first pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabayotu","text_ar":"جَبَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Zj, TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He appropriated"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"purely to himself, exclusively of any partner; chose"},{"kind":"text","text":"it, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in preference, for himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, TA.) And hence, (Zj, TA,) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AjtbAhu","text_ar":"اجتباهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He chose it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"selected it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, S, K)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"linafosihi","text_ar":"لِنَفْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaY","text_ar":"جَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaA","text_ar":"جَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabaA^a","text_ar":"جَبَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He returned, receded, retreated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went back."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Ks","S","Sh","Msb","Zj"]},{"entry_id":"n5025","headword_ar":"جبّى","root":"jbw and jbY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajobiyapN","text_ar":"تَجْبِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He placed his hands upon his knees,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) in prayer; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he fell prostrate;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fell upon his face:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lowered his body and his hands, and raised his buttocks:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 801:) [or]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tjbyp","text_ar":"تجبية"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"standing [with the hands upon the knees] in the manner of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raAkiE","text_ar":"رَاكِع"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K: *) accord. to A'Obeyd, what is thus termed is of two kinds: one is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"placing the hands upon the knees, while standing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the other, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prostrating oneself,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falling upon the face, lying down;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sujuwdN","text_ar":"سُجُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bending down, and placing the hands upon the knees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it is a bringing-together of the limbs. (Mgh.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jb~Ahu","text_ar":"جبّاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is vulgar. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S"]}]}}